description: Erection of a 42 storey building comprising a hotel at ground to 6th floor (12,689 sq m) with between 145 and 155 bedrooms, a restaurant (Class A3) at 7th floor level (564 sq m), 248 residential units at 8th to 41st floor (25,847 sq m) and 222 sq m of flexible Class A1-A4 floorspace at ground floor, together with associated amenity space, landscaping, plant and ancillary works.
